Gently press either side of the screen to turn pages using PagePress. Press the line to page forwards. Press the dot to page backwards.
Tap the top of the screen to display the toolbar.
To page forward in a book, press the top button. To go to the previous page, press the bottom button.
You’ve turned your first page! Tap on the right side of the screen to turn the next page. Tap on the left side of the screen to go back a page.
